#!/bin/bash

cat <<-EOF

This is quick and dirty 'crontab' format help.
See 'crontab(5)' for more details.

The time and date fields are:

    field           allowed values
    -----           --------------
    minute          0-59
    hour            0-23
    day of month    1-31
    month           1-12 (or names, see below)
    day of week     0-7 (0 or 7 is Sunday, or use names)

EOF
